title: I just want to talk to an agent about unemployment desperate
text: Ive been unemployed since march 9. I didnt meet the 680 hours originally for the last quarter (i was at 652) but since april 13, i meet the criteria now. Regardless, i have been filing since march 9 and only have an active claim for last week and all the other claims are “invalid” when will these be paid? And will it qualify for the +600?
